text:
Feedback Questionnaire – Wikimedia Conference 2018 
 
Email 
Dear participants of the Wikimedia Conference, 
  
Thank you all for joining us here in Berlin and for your participation in the Wikimedia Conference!  
To improve future Wikimedia Conferences and also share lessons learned with other Wikimedia event 
organizers, we appreciate your comments and feedback.  
  
Please follow this link to fill in the feedback survey, which takes ​around 10 to 15 minutes​: 
 
Take the Survey 
 
Or copy and paste the URL below into your internet browser: 
LINK 
 
Best regards, 
Cornelius 
 
Cornelius Kibelka 
Program and Engagement Coordinator (PEC) 
for the Wikimedia Conference 
 
 
Dear participants of the Wikimedia Conference 2018, 
Please take a few minutes to give us your valuable feedback on the conference! By filling in this
 
  
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
feedback form, you will help to improve the quality and impact of the Wikimedia Conference in the
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
  
 
future. We explicitly encourage you to express also critical feedback - if applicable - to gain a
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
   
  
 
  
realistic picture of the strengths or weaknesses of the conference. The data from this survey will be
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
processed statistically and the results will be published only in an aggregated form, which means
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
that there will be no possibility to identify you or your individual answers. All responses are
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
optional.
